Variable Documentation

$LD_ddpMMpyyyy = 'dd.mm.gggg'

The following lines must be modified according to the examples: english: day = d , month = m, year = y result => dd.mm.yyyy

german: day = t, month = m, year = j result => tt.mm.jjjj

indonesian: day = h, month = b, year = t result => hh.bb.tttt
